Command> colcon build --symlink-install  # パッケージを自動的にインストール

Description>
           >
           > Since build types such as ament_cmake do not support the concept of the devel space and require the package to be installed, colcon supports the option --symlink-install
           > ament_cmakeはパッケージのインストールができなかった模様
           > e.g.
           > $ git clone https://github.com/ros2/examples src/examples -b humble
           > colcon build --symlink-install


Reference> https://docs.ros.org/en/humble/Tutorials/Beginner-Client-Libraries/Colcon-Tutorial.html 

